OL,5,G2200 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,6,     FAdam, 42, has a broken leg after a
OL,7,     Ffall at work, 22-year-old Luke has
OL,8,     Fa potentially life-threatening
OL,9,     Firregular heartbeat, and a child
OL,10,     Fstops breathing after a seizure.
OL,11,G2300 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,12,     FCritical care teams race to save
OL,13,     Flives as a 61-year-old is injured
OL,14,     Fin a motorcycle crash, a new mum
OL,15,     Fhaemorrhages days after giving
OL,16,     Fbirth, and a 12-year-old suffers
OL,17,     Fsevere leg injuries.
