OL,5,G0000 A&E After Dark
OL,6,     FA patient brought into A&E by
OL,7,     Fpolice claims to have swallowed
OL,8,     Fdrugs, but he refuses to
OL,9,     Fco-operate with staff, putting the
OL,10,     FNHS under further pressure.
OL,11,G0100 #Text Me When You Get Home
OL,12,     FHannah Anderson's best friend
OL,13,     Frealises something is wrong when
OL,14,     FHannah stops responding to her
OL,15,     Ftexts, but no one knows that
OL,16,     FHannah has been abducted by
OL,17,     Fsomeone close to her.
