OL,5,G0155 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FFour top dermatologists treat
OL,7,     Fpatients for skin conditions such
OL,8,     Fas cysts, lipomas and skin tags
OL,9,     Fthat the NHS views as cosmetic,
OL,10,     Fbut that can hugely affect the
OL,11,     Fsufferers.
OL,12,G0245 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,13,     FThis week the staff at the Hall
OL,14,     FGreen Health Centre in Birmingham
OL,15,     Fare getting ready for another busy
OL,16,     Fweek.
